### Get all Books first to grab a real ID (copy one ID from the response below)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books
Authorization: Basic alice:alice

###

### Restock a book — happy path
### IsActiveEntity=true is required because Books is draft-enabled — its real key is (ID, IsActiveEntity).
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(ID=7030288e-fdc4-46e0-af1c-8d5cff39cc6f,IsActiveEntity=true)/CatalogService.restock
Authorization: Basic alice:alice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 20
}

###

### Restock with invalid quantity — should return 400 from OUR validation
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(ID=7030288e-fdc4-46e0-af1c-8d5cff39cc6f,IsActiveEntity=true)/CatalogService.restock
Authorization: Basic alice:alice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": -5
}

###

### Restock a non-existent book — should return 404 from OUR handler
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(ID=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000,IsActiveEntity=true)/CatalogService.restock
Authorization: Basic alice:alice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 10
}

###

### Call getStockValue function — happy path
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(ID=7030288e-fdc4-46e0-af1c-8d5cff39cc6f,IsActiveEntity=true)/CatalogService.getStockValue()
Authorization: Basic alice:alice

###

### Call getStockValue on non-existent book — should return 404 from OUR handler
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(ID=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000,IsActiveEntity=true)/CatalogService.getStockValue()
Authorization: Basic alice:alice

###

### Negative check: bob (reader role) should be FORBIDDEN from restock — 403 expected, correct reason this time (role mismatch, not a missing grant)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(ID=7030288e-fdc4-46e0-af1c-8d5cff39cc6f,IsActiveEntity=true)/CatalogService.restock
Authorization: Basic bob:bob
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 5
}

###

### Negative check: bob (reader role) SHOULD be allowed to call getStockValue, since we granted it to 'any'
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(ID=7030288e-fdc4-46e0-af1c-8d5cff39cc6f,IsActiveEntity=true)/CatalogService.getStockValue()
Authorization: Basic bob:bob